1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:14,926
Said I was gluten-free last fall at school

2
00:00:15,076 --> 00:00:25,003
Now I pack my snacks and follow the rule

3
00:00:25,153 --> 00:00:35,079
My friends all nod like they understand

4
00:00:35,229 --> 00:00:45,155
I pass on the pizza and play it bland

5
00:00:45,305 --> 00:00:55,231
Pretending’s easy once you’ve begun

6
00:00:55,381 --> 00:01:05,308
They bring me rice cakes by the ton

7
00:01:05,458 --> 00:01:15,384
I fake a frown, but truth be said—

8
00:01:15,534 --> 00:01:25,460
I kinda like the gluten-free bread

9
00:01:25,610 --> 00:01:35,537
No one asked, I just went along

10
00:01:35,687 --> 00:01:45,613
Now it’s quinoa chips and chickpea song

11
00:01:45,763 --> 00:01:55,689
I miss the wheat, but not with dread

12
00:01:55,839 --> 00:02:05,765
‘Cause I kinda like the gluten-free bread

13
00:02:05,915 --> 00:02:15,842
I dodge the bread line with quiet grace

14
00:02:15,992 --> 00:02:25,918
Skip every crust, keep a straight face

15
00:02:26,068 --> 00:02:35,994
It’s spongy, crumbly, not the best—

16
00:02:36,144 --> 00:02:46,071
But I’m still not unimpressed

17
00:02:46,221 --> 00:02:56,147
I never meant to lie, not deep

18
00:02:56,297 --> 00:03:06,223
Just wanted in, a tribe to keep

19
00:03:06,373 --> 00:03:16,299
Now flaxseed wraps are in my head

20
00:03:16,449 --> 00:03:26,376
And I kinda like the gluten-free bread

21
00:03:26,526 --> 00:03:36,452
No one asked, I just went along…
